1. Prethodno *sam se raspitao o kvalitetu ovog proizvoda. (Previously, I inquired about the quality of this product.)
2. Da bismo uspeli, *prethodno moramo napraviti plan. (In order to succeed, we must first make a plan.)
3. *Prethodnoj godini sam imao mnogo više obaveza. (Last year, I had a lot more responsibilities.)
4. Molim vas da *prethodno rezervišete mesto u restoranu. (Please make a reservation at the restaurant in advance.)
5. Ako *prethodno ne uplatite račun, usluga neće biti aktivna. (If you don't pay the bill beforehand, the service won't be active.)
6. Rešenje problema je bilo *prethodno testirano. (The solution to the problem had been previously tested.)
7. *Prethodno ste dobili upozorenje, ne mogu vam dozvoliti da nastavite sa kršenjem pravila. (You have previously been warned, I cannot allow you to continue breaking the rules.)
8. Pre nego što odemo, *prethodno ćemo pozvati taksi. (Before we leave, we will call a taxi beforehand.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "prethodno" can be used as an adverb or as an adjective in different positions in a sentence, and it usually means "previously", "beforehand", or "prior".